      <title>朝日新闻称，日本将考虑允许扩建核电站</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/japan-to-consider-allowing-nuclear-plant-expansions-asahi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《朝日新闻》报道，日本经济产业省正在考虑允许扩建核电站，因为老核电站正在逐步退役。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/japan-to-consider-allowing-nuclear-plant-expansions-asahi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 01:36:10 GMT</pubDate>
